<br>
We even asked if we could have Byg Benn (the clockwork dragon) released in order to defend, but again, Verant denies us.<br>
<br>
And if Baron Apep declines to appear for the raid at the time of his choosing, it will show cowardice on his part. He is commited and we expect him to stand by his word, lest it become worthless.Apep has said that it was up to the individual on how they choose to fight. And I think many would choose NOT to fight those of us who stand at the gates because they would rather have the easier prey behind us.<br>
<br>
It boggles the mind how so many can rally to his cause solely to cause death without any rewards, save for a rusty sword or a piece of scrap metal. Possibly for even a few rare silver coin, a defender's life savings.<br>
<br>
So to hell with your condemnation of our defense of Ak'Anon. You are in OUR world now.<br>
<br>
Xianya Lilboomer<br>
